 digiKam 7.0.0 - Release date: 2019-xx-xx

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

FaceManagement: New Neural Network engine based on OpenCV to detect and recognize faces.
SlideShow     ; Add new shuffle mode.
HTMLGallery   : Add new theme "Html5Responsive".
General       : Update internal libraw engine to last 201910 snapshot (https://www.libraw.org/news/libraw-snapshot-201910)

*****************************************************************************************************
